<h1>Managing system packages/applications</h1>

<p>
  To add a repository, simply clone and add the directory name to a list.
</p>

<pre class="code">
git clone --recursive https://github.com/username/package-repository src/packages/package-repository
</pre>

<p>
  Then simply add it to the "repositories" array in <i>src/conf/000-base.json</i> (or <a href="/doc/manuals/man-configuration.html">create your own configuration file</a>)
</p>

<p>
  If you want to remove a repository, simply delete the directory or remove it from the list
</p>

